Description:
Fantastic Court Location - 801m2 Of Land
Tucked away in a beautiful and quiet court is where you will find this neat 4 bedroom family home which offers many things that you won't find in other homes.
Conveniently positioned within close proximity to everything that makes Keilor Downs so popular, this home is best remembered by its conventional and open floor-plan and the generous block size that is on offer. Without doubt, 7 Alawa Court offers the perfect mix of space, location and undeniable value!
Property Features:
* 4 bedrooms - Master bedroom with full ensuite and walk in robe
* Formal lounge upon entry
* The best of open plan living which incorporates a large central kitchen with quality 900mm appliances, sunlit meals zone with garden outlook and large everyday living room
* Large undercover outdoor entertaining area, perfect for all season use
* Double garage with internal home access and rear yard access
* All set on a neatly landscaped block of land that measures approximately 801m2
Sale Includes: Ducted heating, evaporative cooling, alarm, auto garage, ceiling fans, garden shed and cubby house.
There's something here for every member of your family!

Description:
SOLD AT AUCTION 3 BUYERS MISSED OUT MORE WANTED!
Dreams can come true - A wonderful opportunity to clinch an original delight! Well placed and beautifully maintained while further boasting a very convenient location, this first choice offering would be a terrific prospect to leap into the market and add your own personal touches to truly make it your own.
In a sensational pocket for families just a few minutes' walk to the upgraded Ginifer train station, Sunshine Hospital, Jackson School, Holy Eucharist Primary, Victoria University, the location is ideal for those wanting convenience at their fingertips. Stroll up the road for a coffee, restaurant, lunch or dinner at the famous Alfrieda Shopping Village, and easy access to the city via Western Ring Road, or Tullamarine Freeway
Showcasing three generous bedrooms with BIR's served by a stunning central spa bathroom, separate toilet plus a discrete laundry. A master bedroom with dual build in wardrobes and ensuite. Enhanced with a spacious step-down family/meals area adjoining the kitchen detailed with timber cabinet linking through to the generous light-filled formal lounge.
More key features include mirrored robes, ducted heating, air conditioning, dishwasher, Terracotta roof, lock-up brick garage and long driveway with ample off-street parking.
Nothing to do but relax in the Spa!

Description:
Corner a brilliant opportunity near everything.
Making its market debut, this supremely spacious two bedroom home presides over a corner allotment of approximately 563m2.
